@{PARD}
@{B}Unguarded Treasure Table Description:@{UB}@{PAR}

Unguarded Treasure Tables appear to be just that - tables.  That is, furniture.
They are either 3' square or 3' diameter tables, suitable for a dining room.@{PAR}

They are, however, not what they seem. They are actually highly magical beings
that wander dungeons in search of unguarded treasure, which they eat.@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

